# Grab new CV

When the user says **"grab new cv"** (or similar: update CV, sync CV, refresh CV PDF):

1. Copy the source file (overwrite destination):
   ```bash
   cp -f /Users/zno/CV/cv-opt/portfolio/zarni_nway_oo_cv.pdf /Users/zno/Portfolio/zno_portfolio/public/zarni_nway_oo_cv.pdf
   ```
2. Confirm both files match (same size or SHA256).
3. Do **not** change `app/page.tsx` or add cache-busting query strings unless the user asks.
4. Remind the user to commit and push `public/zarni_nway_oo_cv.pdf` if they want it live on GitHub Pages.

**Source of truth:** `/Users/zno/CV/cv-opt/portfolio/zarni_nway_oo_cv.pdf` (cv-opt project).  
**Site file:** `public/zarni_nway_oo_cv.pdf` (served at `/zarni_nway_oo_cv.pdf`).
